      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  KEY ITEM PROCESSING                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         $SB210    BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTAHDPW601
     C                     SETOF                     3132
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    @ERR
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    @@MSG
